              ),
            ],
          ),
          child: Row(
            children: [
              Container(
                padding: const EdgeInsets.all(6),
                decoration: BoxDecoration(
                  color: Colors.red.shade100,
                  borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(8),
                  boxShadow: [
                    BoxShadow(
                      color: Colors.red.withOpacity(0.2),
                      blurRadius: 4,
                      offset: const Offset(0, 2),
